783/kasus-wni-positif-corona-melonjak-dari-227-jadi-309|title=Kasus WNI Positif Corona Melonjak dari 227 Jadi 309|last=Sidik|first=Farih Maulana|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref> However, it is revised to 308 cases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbcindonesia.com/news/20200319182124-4-146252/pemerintah-meralat-kasus-positif-corona-di-ri-jadi-308-kasus|title=Pemerintah Meralat: Kasus Positif Corona di RI Jadi 308 Kasus|last=dob|website=news|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>\n*4 more patients in DKI Jakarta announced cured from COVID-19.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2020/03/19/16104301/update-15-orang-dinyatakan-sembuh-dari-covid-19|title=UPDATE: 15 Orang Dinyatakan Sembuh dari Covid-19|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|website=Kompas.com|language=id|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n*The import of Rapid Test Tools (15 minutes - 3 hours) by [[:id:Rajawali Nusantara Indonesia|Rajawali Nusantara Indonesia]] from China has been approved by [[Ministry of Health (Indonesia)|Ministry of Health]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.detik.com/berita-ekonomi-bisnis/d-4945868/alat-cek-virus-corona-15-menit-mulai-masuk-ke-ri-hari-ini|title=Alat Cek Virus Corona 15 Menit Mulai Masuk ke RI Hari Ini|last=Afriyadi|first=Achmad Dwi|website=detikfinance|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.detik.com/berita-ekonomi-bisnis/d-4944943/ri-mau-beli-alat-tes-corona-secepat-kilat-buatan-china|title=RI Mau Beli Alat Tes Corona 'Secepat Kilat' Buatan China|last=Afriyadi|first=Achmad Dwi|website=detikfinance|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n* President Joko Widodo and wife, [[Iriana]], tested negative on the COVID-19 test.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4945942/jokowi-saya-dan-ibu-iriana-alhamdulillah-negatif-corona|title=Jokowi: Saya dan Ibu Iriana Alhamdulillah Negatif Corona|last=Erwanti|first=Marlinda Oktavia|website=Detik.com|language=id-ID|access-date=20